---
// Neighborhood landing page for Wilderness Lake Preserve, Land O' Lakes.
// Targets pine sap, bird dropping etching, and spring/fall pollen specific to heavy canopy communities.
import BaseLayout from '@/components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '@/components/ui/Button.astro';
import Divider from '@/components/ui/Divider.astro';
import Pause from '@/components/ui/Pause.astro';
import RelatedBlogBox from '@/components/sections/RelatedBlogBox.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@graph': [
    {
      '@type': ['LocalBusiness', 'AutoWash', 'ProfessionalService'],
      '@id': 'https://bayshine.net/#business',
      name: 'BayShine Detailing',
      telephone: '+18133245522',
      url: 'https://bayshine.net',
      address: {
        '@type': 'PostalAddress',
        addressLocality: "Land O' Lakes",
        addressRegion: 'FL',
        postalCode: '34638',
        addressCountry: 'US',
      },
      areaServed: {
        '@type': 'City',
        name: "Land O' Lakes",
        containsPlace: { '@type': 'Neighborhood', name: 'Wilderness Lake Preserve' },
      },
    },
    {
      '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
      itemListElement: [
        { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://bayshine.net' },
        { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: "Land O' Lakes", item: 'https://bayshine.net/land-o-lakes' },
        { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 3, name: 'Wilderness Lake Preserve', item: 'https://bayshine.net/land-o-lakes/wilderness-lake-preserve' },
      ],
    },
  ],
};
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Auto Detailing in Wilderness Lake Preserve, Land O' Lakes | BayShine"
  description="Mobile auto detailing in Wilderness Lake Preserve, Land O' Lakes. BayShine handles pine sap, bird dropping etching, and heavy pollen from the canopy. Exterior detail, full detail, ceramic coating, and the Standing Detail program."
  canonical="https://bayshine.net/land-o-lakes/wilderness-lake-preserve"
  schema={schema}
  keywords="auto detailing Wilderness Lake Preserve, mobile detailing Land O Lakes FL, car detailing tree sap pollen"
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="noise-overlay py-24 px-4 min-h-[60vh] flex flex-col justify-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="text-bay-gold text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">WILDERNESS LAKE PRESERVE, LAND O' LAKES, FL</p>
        <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-bay-white leading-[1.08] mb-6 tracking-tight" style="text-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(15,27,45,0.7);">
          Mobile auto detailing.<br />Wilderness Lake Preserve.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-bay-slate text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl">
          Wilderness Lake Preserve's heavy tree canopy creates three distinct contamination threats that each require different chemistry to remove: pine sap, bird droppings, and seasonal pollen. Each one does different damage to clear coat, each one bonds faster in Florida heat, and each one has a window for correct removal before the damage becomes permanent. The window is shorter than most people realize.
        </p>
        <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" class="text-base px-8 py-3.5">
          Schedule a Service in Wilderness Lake Preserve
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Divider />

  <!-- WHY IT MATTERS -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="reveal mb-12">
        <p class="text-bay-gold text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">WHAT'S HAPPENING TO YOUR PAINT</p>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-bay-white leading-tight">
          Three conditions every Wilderness Lake Preserve vehicle faces.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 reveal">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-bay-gold pl-5">
          <p class="font-semibold text-bay-white text-sm mb-2">Pine sap — a shrinking removal window</p>
          <p class="text-bay-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Fresh pine sap is tacky and lifts with a proper clay bar. Sap that has been sitting in Florida heat for three to five days begins to polymerize and bond to the clear coat surface. After a week, removal without paint correction is often not possible. The canopy at Wilderness Lake Preserve drops sap year-round — not just in spring. Frequency matters here.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-bay-gold pl-5">
          <p class="font-semibold text-bay-white text-sm mb-2">Bird dropping etching</p>
          <p class="text-bay-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Bird droppings are uric acid. In Pasco County summer heat, the acid activates quickly against clear coat. A dropping left overnight on a hot horizontal panel can leave a permanent etch mark. pH-neutral chemistry, applied without delay, is the only correct response. Wiping dry creates micro-scratches on top of the etch.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-bay-gold pl-5">
          <p class="font-semibold text-bay-white text-sm mb-2">Pollen season timing</p>
          <p class="text-bay-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Wilderness Lake Preserve sits under heavy oak and pine coverage. The spring pollen event runs March through May — fine particles that settle into every surface gap and become mildly acidic in humidity. A second, lighter event hits in September. The Standing Detail's 6-week cycle is timed specifically to address both events before the next accumulation begins.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Divider />

  <!-- STANDING DETAIL -->
  <section class="noise-overlay section-bevel bg-bay-deep py-20 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="text-bay-gold text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">RECURRING PROTECTION</p>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-bay-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          The Standing Detail program.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-bay-slate text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-2xl">
          Under a canopy like Wilderness Lake Preserve's, the damage from inaction compounds faster than anywhere else in Land O' Lakes. Sap hardens, droppings etch, pollen acidifies — each on its own schedule, not yours. The Standing Detail's 6-week cycle keeps the removal window open. You don't need to schedule; the slot is already held.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10">
          {[
            { label: 'Priority Slot', desc: 'Your recurring time is held. No competing for availability.' },
            { label: 'Locked Rate', desc: 'The price you start at is the price you keep.' },
            { label: 'Cancel Anytime', desc: 'No contracts. No cancellation fee. No pressure.' },
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="border-l-2 border-bay-gold pl-5">
              <p class="font-semibold text-bay-white text-sm mb-1">{item.label}</p>
              <p class="text-bay-slate text-sm">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <Button href="/standing-detail" variant="primary" class="text-base px-8 py-3.5">
          How the Program Works
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Pause />

  <Divider />

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="reveal mb-12">
        <p class="text-bay-gold text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">SERVICES</p>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-bay-white leading-tight">
          What we offer in Wilderness Lake Preserve.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 reveal">
        {[
          {
            name: 'Exterior Detail',
            desc: 'Iron decontamination, synthetic clay bar, two-stage wash, polymer sealant. Removes sap, pollen, and embedded contamination from the full exterior.',
            href: '/exterior-detail',
          },
          {
            name: 'Full Detail',
            desc: 'Complete interior and exterior. Decontamination, clay, sealant, and a thorough interior clean — pollen and fine debris accumulate inside too.',
            href: '/full-detail',
          },
          {
            name: 'Ceramic Coating',
            desc: 'Nano-silica coating bonded to clear coat. Hydrophobic surface makes sap and droppings easier to remove before they bond. UV protection built in.',
            href: '/ceramic-coating',
          },
          {
            name: 'Heavy Reconditioning',
            desc: 'For vehicles where sap, etching, or oxidation have already caused surface damage. Paint correction included in recon scope.',
            href: '/recon',
          },
        ].map(service => (
          <a
            href={service.href}
            class="group block border border-bay-slate/20 hover:border-bay-gold/50 bg-bay-deep/40 hover:bg-bay-deep/60 rounded-sm p-6 transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-bay-gold"
          >
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-bay-white text-lg mb-2">{service.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-bay-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">{service.desc}</p>
            <span class="text-bay-gold text-sm font-medium group-hover:underline underline-offset-4">Learn more &rarr;</span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Divider />

  <RelatedBlogBox topic="general" />

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="noise-overlay bg-bay-deep py-20 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-bay-white mb-4">
          Schedule a service in Wilderness Lake Preserve.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-bay-slate mb-8">
          Call or text (813) 324-5522, or book online. We respond within 2 hours.
        </p>
        <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" class="text-base px-8 py-3.5">
          Book Now
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
